ew, low-ceremony way to build small HTTP APIs using ASP.NET Core. The demo includes a Blazor app.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-11-12T20:33:08.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Videos</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3LJDMAOm8JU\">Blazor Hot Reload in .NET 6</a> - <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Duration:%20-5%20min-%230094FF?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=maxAge&#x26;logo=youtube\" alt=\"duration\"> November 9, 2021 - With Blazor Hot Reload, you can save time by seeing your ASP.NET WebAssembly apps changes live! Here, Isadora will demo how to use this time and expense saving feature so you can make your WebAssembly apps even more awesome.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-11-12T16:32:17.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Videos</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jte_VwsSazs\">Smaller &#x26; Faster Blazor WebAssembly apps with Runtime Relinking in .NET 6</a> - <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Duration:%20-2%20min-%230094FF?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=maxAge&#x26;logo=youtube\" alt=\"duration\"> November 9, 2021 - The new support for runtime relinking has made Blazor WebAssembly apps smaller and faster to download. In this demo, Daniel Roth will show how runtime relinking works while making the smallest WebAssembly app possible.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-11-12T16:32:17.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Videos</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9RNWAF9SKO0\">Blazor WebAssembly AOT on Azure Static Web Apps in .NET 6</a> - <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Duration:%20-3%20min-%230094FF?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=maxAge&#x26;logo=youtube\" alt=\"duration\"> November 9, 2021 - Host your Blazor WebAssembly applications on Azure Static Web Apps. Anthony Chu will demo how to automatically build and deploy your app, utilize <a href=\"https://get.dot.net/6\">.NET 6</a>, and improve your runtime performance with ahead-of-time compilation on Azure Static Web Apps.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-11-12T16:32:17.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Videos</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RZhEScjKVHE\">Full-stack .NET with Blazor WebAssembly and Azure Static Web Apps</a> - <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Duration:%20-27%20min-%230094FF?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=maxAge&#x26;logo=youtube\" alt=\"duration\"> November 11, 2021 - With automatic global distribution, custom domains, and free SSL certificates, Azure Static Web Apps has everything you need to deploy modern web applications with serverless APIs. Join us to learn all about how to deploy Blazor WebAssembly apps with .NET Azure Functions to Azure Static Web Apps.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-11-12T16:28:40.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Videos</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kesUNeBZ1Os\">New Blazor WebAssembly capabilities in .NET 6</a> - <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Duration:%20-29%20min-%230094FF?style=flat-square&#x26;cacheSeconds=maxAge&#x26;logo=youtube\" alt=\"duration\"> November 10, 2021 - With <a href=\"https://get.dot.net/6\">.NET 6</a>, the underlying .NET WebAssembly runtime supports entirely new kinds of functionality, and can be faster and more productive than ever before. \"Native dependencies\" enables embedding libraries from other tech stacks (e.g., a C/C++ database engine, or a Rust media processor). AOT compilation brings truly near-native performance to your .NET code in the browser, and the new build toolchain can now strip out unused native code to ship significantly smaller bundles. This talk explores how you can build new kinds of web apps, while having a more enjoyable and productive experience via instant hot reload and a better Razor editor.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-11-12T16:28:40.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"playcanvas/awesome-playcanvas","categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactive Experiences</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://hntsam.com/\">How Not To Suck At Money</a> - Educational game from Invesco about personal finance.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-11-12T15:29:51.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"rust-embedded/awesome-embedded-rust","categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/auxoncorp/ferros\">ferros</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/auxoncorp/ferros\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">59</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":59,\"repo\":\"auxoncorp/ferros\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> A Rust-based userland which also adds compile-time assurances to seL4 development.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-11-12T14:56:00.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"awesome-selfhosted/awesome-selfhosted","categoryHTML":"<h2>Software</h2><h3>Media Streaming - Video Streaming</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/owncast/owncast\">Owncast</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/owncast/owncast\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-